Mƒõjme n√°hodn√Ω vektor \(\mathbf X = (Y, Z)^T\) s diskr√©tn√≠m rozdƒõlen√≠m, p≈ôiƒçem≈æ veliƒçina \(Y\) nab√Ωv√° hodnot \(1, \dots, r\) a veliƒçina \(Z\) nab√Ωv√° hodnot \(1, \dots, c\). Oznaƒçme sdru≈æen√© pravdƒõpodobnosti\[p_{ij} = \operatorname P(Y = i \cap Z = j)\]a margin√°ln√≠ pravdƒõpodobnosti\[\begin{align}
p_{i \bullet} = \displaystyle \sum_j p_{ij}, \\
p_{\bullet j} = \displaystyle \sum_i p_{ij}. \\
\end{align}\]D√°le mƒõjme n√°hodn√Ω v√Ωbƒõr \(X_1, \dots, X_n\) z rozdƒõlen√≠ vektoru \(\mathbf X\). ƒåetnosti \(N_{ij}\) dvojic hodnot \((i, j)\) tohoto n√°hodn√©ho v√Ωbƒõru pak maj√≠ sdru≈æen√© multinomick√© rozdƒõlen√≠ s pravdƒõpodobnostmi \(p_{ij}\), kde\[N_{ij} = |\{ k \mid Y_k = i \cap Z_k = j \}|.\]Sestavme n√°hodnou matici \(\mathbf N\) rozmƒõru \(r \times c\) se slo≈ækami \(N_{ij}\), kterou budeme naz√Ωvat kontingenƒçn√≠ tabulkou, a definujme margin√°ln√≠ ƒçetnosti\[\begin{align}
N_{i \bullet} = \displaystyle \sum_j N_{ij}, \\
N_{\bullet j} = \displaystyle \sum_i N_{ij}.
\end{align}\]Pro test nez√°vislosti v kontingenƒçn√≠ tabulce p≈ôi hypot√©ze\[H_0: p_{ij} = p_{i \bullet} p_{\bullet j} \quad \text{proti} \quad H_A: p_{ij} \neq p_{i \bullet} p_{\bullet j}\]pou≈æijeme \(\chi^2\) test dobr√© shody p≈ôi \((r - 1) + (c - 1)\) nezn√°m√Ωch parametrech. Odhady marign√°ln√≠ch pravdƒõpodobnost√≠ metodou minim√°ln√≠ho \(\chi^2\) jsou:\[\begin{align}
\hat p_{i \bullet} &= \frac{N_{i \bullet}} n,\\
\hat p_{\bullet j} &= \frac{N_{\bullet j}} n.
\end{align}\]Dosazen√≠m do testov√© statistiky \(\chi^2\) testu dobr√© shody dostaneme testovou statistiku:\[\chi^2 = \displaystyle \sum_{i = 1}^r \displaystyle \sum_{j = 1}^c \frac{\Big( N_{ij} - n \hat p_{i \bullet} \hat p_{\bullet j} \Big)^2}{n \hat p_{i \bullet} \hat p_{\bullet j}} = \displaystyle \sum_{i = 1}^r \displaystyle \sum_{j = 1}^c \frac{\Big( N_{ij} - \frac{N_{i \bullet} N_{\bullet j}}{n} \Big)^2}{\frac{N_{i \bullet} N_{\bullet j}}{n}}\]Jej√≠ kritick√Ω obor stanov√≠me n√°sledovnƒõ:\[\chi^2 \geq \chi^2_{\alpha, (r - 1) (c - 1)},\]proto≈æe poƒçet stup≈à≈Ø volnosti lze upravit n√°sleduj√≠c√≠m zp≈Øsobem:\[k - m - 1 = rc - \bigl( (r - 1) + (c - 1) \bigr) - 1= (r - 1) (c - 1).\]
